==Preparation==
{{See also|Treasure Trails/Guide/Emote clues/Items}}
[[Clue scroll (hard)|Hard clue scrolls]] can be between four and six clues long, with multiple enemies to defeat and can have high-levelled quest requirements.

{|class="wikitable align-center-1"
! colspan=2 | Item
! Description
|-
| {{plinkt|Clue scroll (hard)|txt=Clue scroll}}
| Must be in the inventory in order to receive the next step or reward.
|-
| {{plinkt|Spade}}
| Digging in certain locations is required for some clues.
|-
| {{plinkp|Law rune}} {{plinkp|Amulet of glory(4)}}
| [[Teleportation]] [[runes]] and enchanted [[jewellery]]
| Use this to travel over large distances.
|-
| {{plinkp|Energy potion}} {{plinkp|Super energy}} {{plinkp|Stamina potion}}
| [[Energy potion]]s ([[Super energy potion|super]]) or [[stamina potion]]s
| Use these to restore [[energy]].
|-
| {{plinkp|Coins|pic=Coins 10000}}
| [[Money]]
| Use this to buy items needed for [[emote clues]] and travel costs.
|-
| {{plinkp|Dramen staff}} {{plinkp|Lunar staff}}
| [[Dramen staff|Dramen]] or [[lunar staff]]
| Use this to access the [[Fairy ring]] network shortly into [[Fairytale II - Cure a Queen]] (especially useful for [[medium clue]]s).
|-
| {{plinkp|Dragon scimitar}} {{plinkp|Black d'hide body}}
| [[Weapon]] and [[armour]]
| Some clue steps require combat.
|-
| {{plinkp|Shark}}
| [[Food]]
| Used to restore [[Hitpoints]].
|-
| {{plinkt|Prayer potion}}s
| Used to restore [[prayer points]].
|-
| {{plinkp|Superantipoison}}
| ([[Superantipoison|Super]]) [[antipoison]] potions
| Use this to cure [[poison]] caused by [[Saradomin wizard]]s.
|-
| {{plinkt|Clue box}}
| Protects clue scrolls while in the wilderness.
|-
| {{plinkt|Wilderness sword 1|txt=Wilderness sword}}
| Wilderness - guaranteed to cut all webs, and clue scrolls are protected over the sword, useful for 3-iteming.
|-
| {{plinkp|Royal seed pod}} {{plinkp|Teleport crystal}}
| [[Royal seed pod]], [[Teleport crystal]]
|
Wilderness - useful teleports especially the Royal Seed pod (can be used below level 30 wilderness);<br>
Clue scrolls are protected over these items, useful for 3-iteming.
|}

